            <title>[LU-8823] remove obsolete OST and MDT thread count parameters</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8823</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Remove obsolete &lt;tt&gt;mdt_num_threads&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;ost_num_threads&lt;/tt&gt; module parameters, since they have been obsolete (and a warning printed if used) since 2.3.  They were only briefly available from 2.0-2.3, and the preferred &lt;tt&gt;mds_num_threads&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;oss_num_threads&lt;/tt&gt; parameters have been around since 1.x times.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
